docblock.description: This Class must be used to create your own activities.
docblock.long-description: Extend it in your own activities and implement the do_activity method

docblock.description: We initialise the Activity in SWF WE check if it is already registered or not If not we register it
We perform basic high level task verifications WE make sure it contains an input and we save it This is the first method to be called when your activity starts
Perform JSON input validation We capture the four keys that compose a CPE Task input
Send SQS notification saying your activity started Implement this method in your activity This is where your logic starts
Activity failed to SQS and SWF Called by ActivityPoller if your activity throws an exeception
Send activity completed to SQS and SWF Called by ActivityPoller once your activity completed
Send heartbeat to SWF to keep the task alive.
docblock.long-description: Timeout is configurable at the Activity level in SWF You must call this regularly within your logic to make sure SWF doesn't consider your activity as 'timeed out'.
